widgets_values: A digital illustration shoot from below about a girl with long, flowing black hair and a red blindfold standing amidst a field of red roses during sunset. the image also shows a dark, moody sky with dark clouds and a distant landscape. on the middle of the image, a 1girl, who appears to be a young woman, standing with her full body facing the viewer, wearing a black dress with red accents. she has a slender physique and a closed mouth, with her hair flowing in the wind. the dress has short sleeves and a lace-up front, and she is wearing a red mask covering her eyes. she is surrounded by red roses, which are scattered around her. the overall style is dark and moody, with a focus on the character and the roses.

nodes.title: Positive prompt
widgets_values: A serene, dreamy scene unfolds against a soft, gradient lapis lazuli sky with layered, symmetrical clouds, and a thick white border, reminiscent of Hayao Miyazaki's whimsical style. A young, blonde-haired, small-breasted girl with pastel cyan eyes and multi-colored twin tails, adorned with hair ornaments, is shot from behind, her long, puffy sleeves and frilled skirt in dark black green hues, with a black bow and laced sleeves, evoking a sense of innocence. She stands amidst a sea of vibrant flowers, as light particles and shooting stars dance around her, imbuing the atmosphere with magic. The warm, golden light of a setting sun casts a gentle glow, with a subtle film grain and muted color grading, evoking a sense of nostalgia and wonder.
